Functionalities
1. MessageId, UserId
2. Http and different storage and web server for media messages
3. Duplex System.
4. Heartbeat for last seen
5. Queue for messages
6. Schedular for backup (configurable)
7. local storage(lightweight) if the system is offline
8. Sync the time with the server
9. Scalable
10. msg character limit is 16 bytes
